Installation
Lobber Storage Node is a plugin for the Twisted framework so there are some
packages that needs to be installed before the storage node can be functional.

For the actual downloading of the torrent data the storage node uses 
Transmission bittorrent client.

  Prerequisites 
    Packages from Debian repositories:
    sudo apt-get install python-twisted-core python-twisted-web python-pip transmission-cli transmission-daemon
    Python modules:
    sudo pip install stompservice feedparser transmissionrpc

  Install
    When the prerequisites are met just run "sudo python setup.py install".

Configuration
See https://portal.nordu.net/display/LOBBER/Running+a+storage+node+%28bud+light%29.
